    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for some TLC and offers a fantastic opportunity for anyone who loves to restore cars to their former glory! While it's currently in rough shape and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it's a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel of this model. It\u2019s an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right owner!",
