    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor surface blemishes and light wear consistent with regular use, while the interior remains clean and comfortable with all major features functioning as intended. Mechanically, it is solid and drives smoothly, making it a dependable choice for any buyer. You can expect a reliable, honest car that has plenty of life left and presents well both inside and out.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both performance and value. Meticulously maintained and appearing in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience supported by a history of consistent care. Every component reflects our commitment to mechanical excellence and aesthetic preservation. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances sophistication with practical longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for all your upcoming adventures! It drives smoothly and has been really well-loved over the years. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a double VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to address known chassis flex issues. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the tactile feedback and lateral stability characteristic of the M-division's peak engineering. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the mechanical integrity is prioritized, featuring refreshed rod bearings and a cooling system overhaul to ensure peak thermal efficiency during spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Used sedan. 48,000 miles. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. No mechanical issues. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of reliability and comfort for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper reflect its honest road history. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with plush seating that shows minimal bolster wear, and all electronic features\u2014including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly, benefited by a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake service. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission shifts crisply through every gear. While there are a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful daily use, the overall presentation is impressive and ready for the commute or a long weekend getaway. This car has been a reliable companion and is looking for a home where its mechanical integrity will be appreciated.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, offering a balance of performance and refined aesthetics. This unit has been subjected to a rigorous professional evaluation, confirming its mechanical soundess and structural integrity. The interior remains in superior condition, reflecting a history of diligent care. Engineered for reliability and comfort, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the serious motorist seeking a dependable daily driver without compromise.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
